'''''Break the Pot''''' is the upcoming second studio album by American rapper [[Rich Boy]]. The album is set to be released on April 9, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|author=Break the Point |url=http://www.amazon.com/Break-Point-Rich-Boy/dp/B0088XQBIQ/ |title=Break the Point: Rich Boy: Music |publisher=Amazon.com |date=March 22, 2013 |accessdate=March 22, 2013}}</ref> The album features [[guest appearance]]s from Mista Raja, [[Maino]], Hemi, GQ Beats, Doe B, Playboi Lo, Smash, Maja, Kaleena, Jue and [[Bobby V]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.de/Break-The-Pot-Explicit/dp/B00BYZ5G8Q/ |title=Break The Pot [Explicit&#93;: Rich Boy: Amazon.de: MP3-Downloads |publisher=Amazon.de |date=March 22, 2013 |accessdate=March 22, 2013}}</ref>

==Background==
On January 14, 2013, the first single was released in promotion of the album titled "Break the Pot" featuring Hemi.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/break-pot-feat.-hemi-single/id593073146 |title=iTunes - Music - Break the Pot (feat. Hemi) - Single by Rich Boy |publisher=Itunes.apple.com |date=January 14, 2013 |accessdate=March 22, 2013}}</ref> On February 25, 2013, it was announced the album would be released on April 9, 2013, and would feature guest appearances from [[Maino]], Mista Raja, [[Bobby V]], Doe B, Playboi Lo and Smash.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xclusiveszone.net/2013/02/rich-boy-announces-break-the-pot-album-release-date/ |title=Rich Boy Announces "Break The Pot" Album Release Date |publisher=Xclusives Zone |date=February 25, 2013 |accessdate=March 22, 2013}}</ref> On March 17, 2013, the music video for "Break the Pot" featuring Hemi premiered on [[MTV Jams]].<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.mtv.com/videos/rich-boy/888932/break-the-pot.jhtml |title=Break The Pot &#124; Rich Boy &#124; Music Video |publisher=MTV |date=March 17, 2013 |accessdate=March 22, 2013}}</ref> On March 18, 2012, Rich Boy released the mixtape ''Back To Class'' in promotion for the album.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rapradar.com/2013/03/18/new-mixtape-rich-boy-back-to-class/ |title=New Mixtape: Rich Boy Back To Class |publisher=Rap Radar |date=March 18, 2013 |accessdate=March 22, 2013}}</ref>

